text: Nick Gleeson (born 18 October 1996) is a British bobsledder. He competed in the four-man event at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:British male bobsledders Category:Olympic bobsledders of Great Britain Category:Bobsledders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
